                "invention-title": [
                    "Hydrogen-heat complementary energy storage type combined heat and power generation system and method",
                    "一种氢-热互补的储能型热电联产系统及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a hydrogen-heat complementary energy storage type combined heat and power generation system and method, and relates to a green low-carbon-emission energy storage type combined heat and power generation system and method. The system comprises a fuel cell power generation unit, a water supply unit, a water supply preheating, temperature rising and pressure rising unit, a high-temperature heat storage steam heat supply unit and a low-temperature heat supply bypass unit. The system has the advantages that hydrogen energy serves as fuel, electric heating heat storage of the heat storage steam heat supply unit is conducted through electric power in the off-peak period, the system is green and low-carbon, battery waste heat is recycled, combined supply of electricity and high-grade steam is achieved, the heat and power cogeneration utilization efficiency is high, and the effect of replacing a traditional coal-fired unit can be achieved; the system is not limited by the heat supply distance, thermoelectric decoupling is achieved, and meanwhile the heat supply economical efficiency is effectively improved; the high-temperature heat storage steam heat supply unit uses three heat storage heat supply methods, and a molten salt system is only used for heating superheated steam, so that the problem of condensation of molten salt can be solved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种氢‑热互补的储能型热电联产系统及方法，涉及绿色低碳排放的储能型热电联产系统和方法。系统包括燃料电池发电单元、给水单元、给水预热升温升压单元、高温蓄热蒸汽供热单元和低温供热旁路单元。本发明系统的优势在于以氢能为燃料，使用低谷时期电力进行蓄热蒸汽供热单元的电加热储热，绿色低碳，对电池余热进行回收利用，实现了电和高品位蒸汽的联合供应，热电联产利用效率高,可以达到替代传统燃煤机组的效果；系统不受供热距离限制，实现热电解耦的同时也有效提高了供热的经济性；高温蓄热蒸汽供热单元使用了三种蓄热供热方法，其中熔盐系统只用于过热蒸汽的加热，可以解决熔盐的冷凝问题。"
                }
            ]
